Ana Girardot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ana_Girardot 0 Ana Girardot (born 1 August 1988) is a French actress. She is best known for her role of Lucy in the television series Les Revenants (The Returned). Ana_Girardot ( born 1_August_1988 ) is a_French_actress .
